    *   The [Muslim Student Followers of the Imam's Line](/Muslim_Student_Followers_of_the_Imam%27s_Line) – The main actors, with the Ayatollah [Ruhollah Khomeini](/Ruhollah_Khomeini) pulling strings from the shadows.
