#### Other Hostages Released After the Crisis

A few individuals, not captured at the embassy, were taken elsewhere in Iran during the same period and released later. This includes businessmen, engineers, reporters, and missionaries. The case of Paul Chiapparone and Bill Gaylord, rescued by a team led by Colonel ["Bull" Simons](/Arthur_D._Simons), funded by [Ross Perot](/Ross_Perot), is particularly noteworthy.

